              "text": "{self.name} kept {rival.name} close the other way — watched, reported on, every move shadowed by people {rival.name} would never spot. {self.name} sleeps easier knowing where the grudge is. {rival.name}, who might have let it fade, will eventually feel the surveillance, and resent it, and become exactly the threat {self.name} was watching for. Suspicion has a way of building its own enemies."
