              "text": "Offered a leap into a different track — a soldier courted for the senate, a steward for the fleet — {self.name} declined and went deeper into the mastery already begun. The realm is full of capable people spread thin across three ambitions. {self.name} chose to be undeniable at one. Depth is its own kind of power, and a rarer one."
