            {
              "type": "log",
              "text": "{self.name} took the leap into the unfamiliar track, trading hard-won seniority for a wider board to play on. The old colleagues called it folly; the old skills count for little in the new arena. But the figure who commands more than one domain frightens those who command only one — and fear, wielded well, is the shortest road to the top of any of them."
            }
          ]
        }
